    "excerpt": "When it comes to tiling your floors, walls, or backsplashes, choosing the suitable, sleek and polished tile is just as important as choosing the suitable grout. Would you agree...",
    "bodyHtml": "<p>When it comes to tiling your floors, walls, or backsplashes, choosing the suitable, sleek and polished tile is just as important as choosing the suitable grout. Would you agree? Outdoor living areas are all about connecting your home with the beauty of the outside world. At <strong>Aushen Stone &amp; Tile</strong>, we make it easy for you to get the perfect outdoor porcelain tiles in Melbourne. Our wide variety of stylish and high-quality tiles are elegant and engineered with remarkable density so you can effortlessly add a touch of sophistication to your outdoor space. Our beautiful <a href=\"https://aushenstone.com.au/outdoorporcelain/\"><b>porcelain pavers in Melbourne</b></a> come in 13 different colours with square shapes, making them easy to design. Here are the primary keys to why our porcelain tiles are perfect for any outdoor surface:</p><ul><li><b>100% Frost-free- </b>The square pavers made in Australia are resistant to water due to their unique clay composition and firing process. <b>They do not even freeze in extreme cold, thus giving you good value for your investment.</b></li><li><b>Remarkable density and unmatched performance -</b> With 20mm thickness, our tiles are highly durable and resistant to cracks. Perfect replacement for a natural stone with an anti-slippery finish.</li><li><b>Ultra-low Wetness absorption- </b>They resist abrasion and keep their beauty very long. After years of use, they will still keep their elegance and texture alive.</li><li><b>Easy to clean- </b>As porcelain pavers are suitable for decking and landscaping, they are easy to clean and maintain. With the aesthetically pleasant appearance, our gorgeous outdoor tiles are apt for areas with high foot traffic.</li></ul><p>From roof decks, terraces, and balconies to walkways and pool-deck areas, Our Aushen Stone &amp; Tile Outdoor complimentary pavers allow a stylish and seamless transition. Offering higher versatility and adaptability, it fits seamlessly with the surrounding nature with various finishes. Our Outdoor Pavers, with innate durability, are suitable for installation in any space. Our wide selection of colours and finishes will blend perfectly with your home’s exterior and interior design. From colours ranging from light to dark, matte to polished, you can select the right one to match the furniture, tiles, and other elements of your space. Each tile is manufactured with an anti-slippery finish for extra safety, so you can ensure a secure footing even when wet. Explore our entire collection at <a href=\"https://aushenstone.com.au/outdoorporcelain/\">https://aushenstone.com.au/outdoorporcelain/</a> to find the perfect fit for your space!</p>",
