    "bodyHtml": "<p>If you have a pool installed in your backyard, you must install quality pool pavers specifically designed to serve as a smooth transition at the edge of your swimming pool. Pool paving separates the exterior of your pool from its interior while providing a great aesthetical point of view.</p><p>It is the first thing people will notice about your pool. Nonetheless, pool paving in Melbourne can be done with a range of materials, such as granite, <a href=\"https://aushenstone.com.au/bluestone/bluestone/\"><strong>bluestone</strong></a>, marble, <a href=\"https://aushenstone.com.au/bluestone/outdoorporcelain/\"><strong>porcelain tile</strong></a> and many more, and you can find pavers in Melbourne that will fit your needs and budget.</p><h2 id=\"top-3-benefits-of-pool-pavers\">Top 3 Benefits Of Pool Pavers</h2><ul><li><b>Durable:</b> Pool pavers can last a lifetime if installed and maintained properly. Because pavers are not made of concrete, they are highly resistant to cracking or deterioration caused by exposure to foot traffic, sun, pool chemicals, salt and other harsh Australian weather conditions.</li></ul><ul><li><b>Maximum Safety:</b> No matter how wet they get, pavers have an anti-slippery surface, providing maximum safety around your swimming pool to children, pets, guests and other family members.</li></ul><ul><li><b>Easily Repairable:</b> In rare instances, if pavers crack or become loose, you can easily repair and replace them at a very low cost. Just remove and replace the individual paver.</li></ul><h3 id=\"why-choose-aushen-stone-andamp-tile\">Why choose Aushen Stone &amp; Tile?</h3><p><strong>Aushen Stone &amp; Tile</strong> is a leading supplier of <a href=\"https://aushenstone.com.au/bluestone/application/pool-coping/\"><strong>pool pavers in Melbourne</strong></a>, offering high-quality products and services at an affordable price. We have a comprehensive range of natural stone pavers, such as travertine, granite, sandstone, marble, porcelain tile and many more, in an exciting range of colours, finishes and textures. With our extensive range of supplies, we are sure that you will find the right pavers to create the perfect pool space.</p><p>To learn more about our products and services, visit our website: <strong>https://aushenstone.com.au/</strong></p>",
