    "excerpt": "There are several reasons why people gravitate toward bluestone tiles in Melbourne . Imagine your backyard garden with a mid-sized patio of bluestone slabs, with a small pool deck...",
    "bodyHtml": "<p>There are several reasons why people gravitate toward <a href=\"https://aushenstone.com.au/bluestone/\"><b>bluestone tiles in Melbourne</b></a>. Imagine your backyard garden with a mid-sized patio of bluestone slabs, with a small pool deck under the blue sky-what an artistic and spectacular view, pleasing you and your guests!</p><p>Bluestone tiles, slabs or veneer is an excellent choice to create a theme for your home exteriors. These stone pavers can be purchased in many country regions, even if the material itself isn&#x27;t natural to that region. The most common ones are:</p><ul><li>Bluestone</li><li>Cobblestone</li><li>Travertine</li></ul><h3 id=\"why-is-bluestone-tiles-a-popular-choice\">Why Is Bluestone Tiles A Popular Choice?</h3><p>Beauty appeal: Bluestone is very aesthetically pleasing. The natural colour and texture variations add natural beauty to your home.</p><p>Strength: It is one of the most favourite materials of Romans. Some roads in Italy paved with this material can still be seen today. People have been using stone pavers for thousands of years as it‘s one of the most durable materials available.</p><p>Design: Stone pavers are available in a variety of sizes, colours, shapes, and textures. One can install them in a number of different patterns, providing many options for your exterior.</p><h3 id=\"suitable-to-use-for\">Suitable to Use For:</h3><p><strong>Pool decks</strong></p><p>A modern pool with geometric texture and colourful chartreuse privacy walls. Bluestone tiles on the pool deck reflect the home&#x27;s architecture, complementing the pool’s design rather than looking like a stand-alone feature.</p><p><strong>Entrance</strong></p><p>The beautiful entryway makes the feel of the home inviting. Bluestone tiles are a perfect choice to create a functional and stylish entryway.</p><p><strong>Driveways</strong></p><p>Compared to ceramic tile, bluestone is harder and durable, making it an ideal choice for high traffic areas-sturdy material resisting breaks and cracks. Bluestone flooring fits the best for busy entryways, especially for areas prone to wet weather.</p><h3 id=\"takeaway\">Takeaway</h3><p>You have ample scope to decorate your home and select from a wide variety of colours, shapes, sizes, and styles of Bluestone tiles. To transform your house into a fresh and modern new look with bluestone tiles in Melbourne, <a href=\"https://aushenstone.com.au/bluestone/\"><b>click here</b>.</a></p>",
